Gravel crunches underfoot—low-frequency noise, short envelope, repeated rhythm.

```scheme
;; Single gravel crunch
(adsr (filter 'lowpass
              (noise 'white 0.15)
              :cutoff 800
              :q 1.5)
      :a 0.01
      :d 0.1
      :s 0.0
      :r 0.05)
```

