## Cymbal Swell — Rising Filter Cutoff

A cymbal swell opens up over time—start with a low cutoff and sweep it upward.

```scheme
;; Cymbal swell — noise with rising cutoff (conceptual)
(adsr (filter 'highpass
              (noise 'white 3.0)
              :cutoff 4000
              :q 1.0)
      :a 0.5
      :d 2.0
      :s 0.2
      :r 0.5)
```

*[needs: adsr-verb, filter-verbs, cutoff-sweep]*  
