## Thunder — Low Rumble with Bandpass Clusters

Thunder is a low rumble with mid-frequency clusters rolling through.

```scheme
;; Thunder rumble — low + mid bandpass layers
(list (adsr (filter 'lowpass
                    (noise 'pink 4.0)
                    :cutoff 150
                    :q 0.5)
            :a 0.2
            :d 2.5
            :s 0.1
            :r 1.5)
      (adsr (filter 'bandpass
                    (noise 'white 4.0)
                    :cutoff 600
                    :q 2.0)
            :a 0.3
            :d 2.0
            :s 0.05
            :r 1.0))
```

*[needs: noise-pink, adsr-verb, filter-verbs]*  
