## Steam Release — Highpass Noise with Fast Decay

Steam hissing from a valve: highpass noise, very fast attack, medium decay.

```scheme
;; Steam hiss
(adsr (filter 'highpass
              (noise 'white 1.5)
              :cutoff 5000
              :q 0.5)
      :a 0.005
      :d 1.2
      :s 0.0
      :r 0.3)
```

