## Brushed Snare — Sustained Noise Layer

A brushed snare drum sweeps bristles across the head—sustained bandpass noise instead of a sharp burst.

```scheme
;; Brushed snare
(adsr (filter 'bandpass
              (noise 'white 0.8)
              :cutoff 3500
              :q 3.5)
      :a 0.02
      :d 0.15
      :s 0.3
      :r 0.5)
