## White Noise Kick — Layering Sub and Noise

Even a kick drum can use noise for the attack click. Layer a very short highpass burst with a low tone.

```scheme
;; Kick drum with noise click
(let ((kick-body (adsr (tone 60 0.4)
                       :a 0.005
                       :d 0.3
                       :s 0.0
                       :r 0.1))
      (kick-click (adsr (filter 'highpass
                                (noise 'white 0.05)
                                :cutoff 6000
                                :q 1.0)
                        :a 0.001
                        :d 0.04
                        :s 0.0
                        :r 0.02)))
  (list kick-body
        (list :gain 0.4 kick-click)))
```

*[needs: adsr-verb, filter-verbs]*  
<!-- BUILD: adsr-verb, filter-verbs, gain/mix -->

