## Shaker — High Noise Bursts at Rhythm

A shaker is high-frequency noise bursts in a rhythmic pattern.

```scheme
;; Single shaker hit
(adsr (filter 'highpass
              (noise 'white 0.1)
              :cutoff 7000
              :q 0.8)
      :a 0.005
      :d 0.06
      :s 0.0
      :r 0.04)
```

