## Tambourine — Noise + Ringing Tone

A tambourine jingles (high noise) and rings (a decaying tone cluster).

```scheme
;; Tambourine hit
(let ((jingle (adsr (filter 'highpass
                            (noise 'white 0.3)
                            :cutoff 8000
                            :q 1.2)
                    :a 0.005
                    :d 0.2
                    :s 0.0
                    :r 0.1))
      (ring (adsr (chord (list 1.0 1.5 2.0))
                  :a 0.01
                  :d 0.25
                  :s 0.0
                  :r 0.15)))
  (list jingle ring))
```

*[needs: adsr-verb, filter-verbs, chord-verb]*  
<!-- BUILD: adsr-verb, filter-verbs, chord-verb (not yet defined in allowlist; may need tone stacking) -->

The `chord` call stacks tones; if unavailable, stack `tone` calls manually.

