## Gong Wash — Filtered Pink Noise with Long Decay

A gong's wash (not the initial strike, but the roar afterward) can be modeled with filtered pink noise and a very long decay.

```scheme
;; Gong wash
(adsr (filter 'lowpass
              (noise 'pink 8.0)
              :cutoff 1200
              :q 2.5)
      :a 0.1
      :d 5.0
      :s 0.1
      :r 3.0)
```

