## Jet Engine — Layered Noise with Subsonic Rumble

A jet engine roars across the frequency spectrum—layer lowpass (rumble), midpass (roar), and highpass (scream).

```scheme
;; Jet engine roar
(list (filter 'lowpass
              (noise 'pink 6.0)
              :cutoff 200
              :q 0.5)
      (filter 'bandpass
              (noise 'white 6.0)
              :cutoff 1500
              :q 1.5)
      (filter 'highpass
              (noise 'white 6.0)
              :cutoff 6000
              :q 0.8))
```

