## Ride Cymbal — Mid-High Bandpass with Ping

A ride cymbal has a \"ping\" (a tone) and a wash (noise).

```scheme
;; Ride cymbal
(let ((ping (adsr (tone 1800 1.0)
                  :a 0.005
                  :d 0.8
                  :s 0.0
                  :r 0.2))
      (wash (adsr (filter 'bandpass
                          (noise 'white 1.0)
                          :cutoff 5000
                          :q 2.0)
                  :a 0.01
                  :d 0.7
                  :s 0.1
                  :r 0.3)))
  (list ping
        (list :gain 0.5 wash)))
```

*[needs: adsr-verb, filter-verbs]*  
<!-- BUILD: adsr-verb, filter-verbs, gain/mix -->

