## Cowbell — Tone Cluster with Noise Click

A cowbell is a cluster of inharmonic tones (not a harmonic series) plus a short noise click at the attack.

```scheme
;; Cowbell
(let ((tones (list (adsr (tone 540 0.5)
                         :a 0.005
                         :d 0.4
                         :s 0.0
                         :r 0.1)
                   (adsr (tone 800 0.5)
                         :a 0.005
                         :d 0.35
                         :s 0.0
                         :r 0.15)))
      (click (adsr (filter 'highpass
                           (noise 'white 0.05)
                           :cutoff 5000
                           :q 1.0)
                   :a 0.002
                   :d 0.03
                   :s 0.0
                   :r 0.02)))
  (list tones
        (list :gain 0.3 click)))
```

*[needs: adsr-verb, filter-verbs]*  
<!-- BUILD: adsr-verb, filter-verbs, gain/mix -->

