## Radio Static Sweep — Bandpass with Swept Cutoff

Tuning a radio dial: bandpass noise with a slowly changing cutoff frequency.

```scheme
;; Radio static (fixed cutoff; sweep needs modulation)
(filter 'bandpass
        (noise 'white 5.0)
        :cutoff 2500
        :q 4.0)
```

*[needs: filter-verbs, cutoff-sweep]*  
<!-- BUILD: filter-verbs, cutoff-sweep -->

