## Percussive Click — Pure Noise, Instant Decay

A percussive click (for a metronome or a hi-hat tick): no filter, just noise, extremely short.

```scheme
;; Click
(adsr (noise 'white 0.05)
      :a 0.001
      :d 0.03
      :s 0.0
      :r 0.02)
```

*[needs: adsr-verb]*  
<!-- BUILD: adsr-verb -->

