## Cable Unplug Pop — Mid Bandpass, Very Short

Unplugging a cable causes a sharp pop—mid-frequency bandpass noise, instant.

```scheme
;; Cable pop
(adsr (filter 'bandpass
              (noise 'white 0.03)
              :cutoff 2200
              :q 2.0)
      :a 0.001
      :d 0.02
      :s 0.0
      :r 0.01)
```

*[needs: adsr-verb, filter-verbs]*  
<!-- BUILD: adsr-verb, filter-verbs -->

