## Whistle Wind — High-Q Bandpass Noise, Sustained

Wind whistling through a gap: high-Q bandpass, sustained with slight swell.

```scheme
;; Wind whistle
(adsr (filter 'bandpass
              (noise 'white 4.0)
              :cutoff 3200
              :q 8.0)
      :a 0.3
      :d 0.5
      :s 0.6
      :r 3.0)
```

*[needs: adsr-verb, filter-verbs]*  
